    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Archaeological or anthropological contexts for accumulations of refuse associated with human occupation. These accumulations may include discarded artifacts and food remains such as bones and shells. They are often used as valuable sources of archaelogical data.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
